item.title: When the 3G iPhone comes out, you'll be just in range (or just out of range)
item.description: The AT&T coverage viewer shows you where your 3G iPhone is going to work in some awesome, inspiring, mind-bogglingly wonderful way. (yeah right). The photo clip above is where it's going to work in Washtenaw County, with the dark blue coverage showing the ideal places.
